modules.description: Runs AWS API requests asynchronously using provided credentials and region. Handles signing and executing AWS service calls for input data types specific to each service. Useful for making authenticated AWS SDK calls like querying S3, DynamoDB, or EC2 APIs from OCaml applications.

Runs AWS API requests asynchronously with credentials and region configuration. Handles signing and execution of service calls for AWS-specific input data types. Enables authenticated SDK calls to services like S3, DynamoDB, and EC2 from OCaml applications.
